"There is something up," thought Nicholas, and he was further confirmed in this conclu- sion by the fact that D61okhov left immediate- ly after dinner. He called Natdsha and asked her what was the matter. 
"And I was looking for you," said Natdsha running out to him. "I told you, but you would not believe it," she said triumphantly. "He has proposed to S6nya!"
